      "text": "念",
      "text_length": 1
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00006",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林冲睡，突醒。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00007",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "那答儿相求救？欲送登高千里目，愁云低锁衡阳路。鱼书不至雁无凭，几番欲作悲秋赋。回首西山日已斜，天涯孤客真难度。丈夫有泪不轻弹，只因未到伤心处。俺林冲。一时愤怒，持剑杀死高俅奸细二贼。多蒙柴大官人赠俺书信一封，荐往梁山。白日不敢行走，只得黑夜而行。呀，适才间星明月朗，一霎时雾暗云迷。看前面黑洞洞，想是人家村庄，待俺趱上前去。𠮾呼呀，我当是人家村庄，原来是座古庙。看门儿半掩半开，待俺挨身而进。黑夜之间，认不出是何神圣。神圣吓神圣。保佑弟子林——唔哼！且喜四顾无人，待俺闭上庙门。神圣吓神圣，保佑弟子林冲，一路无灾无难，早到梁山，借得兵来，报了深仇，自当重修庙宇，再塑金身。嘿，俺的身子有些困倦，不免在神圣案前，打一盹睡，醒来再走。正是：一觉放开心定稳，梦魂千里到阳台。啊呀，唬死我也，吓，吓死我也！适才合眼，分明神圣嘱咐，今有金枪手徐宁，带领官兵五百，追至黄河渡口，特来拿我。此时不走，更待何时。不免拜谢神圣，开了庙门，甩开大步直奔梁山走遭也。（双调新水令）按龙泉血泪洒征袍，恨天涯一身流落。专心投水浒，回首望天朝。急走忙逃，顾不的忠和孝。（驻马听）凉夜迢迢，凉夜迢迢，（夹白）投宿——",
      "text_length": 493
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00008",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "驻马听休将门户敲。遥瞻残月，暗渡重关，急走荒郊。俺的身轻不惮路迢遥，心忙又恐怕人惊觉。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00009",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "吓！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00010",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "驻马听",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "吓得咱魄散魂消，魄散魂消，红尘误了五陵年少。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00011",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "想俺林冲，在那八十万军中，做了禁军教头，征那吐蕃的时节呵！",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00012",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "折桂令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "实指望，封侯学那万里班超，",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00013",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "到如今——",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00014",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "折桂令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "生逼做叛国红巾，做了背主黄巢。恰便似脱扣苍鹰，离笼狡兔，折网腾蛟。救国难谁诛正卯？掌刑法难得皋陶！似这鬓发焦梢，行李萧条。此一去，搏得个斗转天回，",
      "text_length": 73
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00015",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "高俅！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00016",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "折桂令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "管教你海沸山摇。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00017",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "双调雁儿落带得胜令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "望家乡去路遥，望家乡去路遥，想母妻将谁靠？俺这里吉凶未可知，他、他那里生死应难料。呀！吓的俺汗津津身上似汤浇，急煎煎心内似油熬。幼妻室今何在？老萱堂恐丧了！劬劳，父母的恩谁报；悲嚎，叹英雄气怎消，叹英雄气怎消。",
      "text_length": 105
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00018",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "唉呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00019",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "沽美酒带太平令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "怀揣着雪刃刀，怀揣着雪刃刀，行一步唉呀哭号啕。急走羊肠去路遥，",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00020",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "天，天哪！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00021",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "沽美酒带太平令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "适才间明星下照。一霎时云迷雾罩，疏喇喇风吹叶落。震山林声声虎啸，又听得哀哀猿叫。俺呵，吓得俺魂飞胆消，似龙驹奔逃。",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00022",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00023",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "沽美酒带太平令",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "百忙里走不出山前古道。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00024",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "收江南",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "呀！又听得乌鸦阵阵起松梢，数声残角断渔樵。忙投村店伴寂寥。想亲帏梦杳，想亲帏梦杳，顾不得风吹雨打度良宵！",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00025",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "煞尾",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "一宵儿奔走荒郊，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00026",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "穷性命——",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00027",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "煞尾",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "挣出路一条。到梁山借得兵来，",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00028",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "夹白",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "高俅哇贼子！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00029",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "煞尾",
      "speakers": [
        "林冲"
      ],
      "text": "定把你奸臣扫！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901115_e00030",
      "play_id": "70901115",
      "scene_id": "70901115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
